{
  "stem": "1692.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 326.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because nobody else survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they would have survived, I would have known.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were-- the Ukrainians came in the day that they got everybody together, and they were-- they were sleeping in an attic, and just got them all and brought them back to the ghetto together with all the other people, and that's when they were killed.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody else left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were brought back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why I survived because I was hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father made a hiding place under a twin bed, as big as a twin bed in-- in the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had some supplies, didn't last that long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there-- there were eight of us in that hiding place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was my aunt, her five-year-old granddaughter, my two cousins, my father and mother, and my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in that hiding place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot of looting upstairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every once in a while, I would hear some screaming outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Ukrainian would catch somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would-- I don't know exactly where they took them, but I found out later there's a special-- in a special place near there-- near the woods that they made one big hole, grave, and they put everybody who they found there, they bring them there and kill them, and bury them right there.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very difficult in that hiding place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's much easier to live without food than without water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one day, the five-year-old little girl said if you don't give me a drink of water, I'm going to scream.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So having no choice, we gave her urine to drink.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She never asked for another drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
